      "title": "Important notice regarding today's power outage",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lanka Electricity Board has issued a statement that after 6.00 pm today the power cut will not be implemented.",
        "In the said report, the Engineer's Association of the Electricity Board has mentioned that the power cut will not be implemented after 6.00 pm today."
